<section id="funding" class="resourcing">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="heading">Budget &amp; Resourcing</h2>

    <p class="target">Target: <strong>CAD $55,000–$115,000</strong>, shared across two funding streams.</p>

    <div class="funding-grid">
      <div class="funding-block">
        <h3 class="block-title">Participant Co-Funding</h3>
        <p class="block-amount">CAD $30,000–$50,000</p>
        <p class="block-description">
          Pay-what-you-can, targeting 3–5 organizations at ~$10K each.
        </p>
        <div class="benefits">
          <p class="benefits-label">Co-funders receive:</p>
          <ul class="benefits-list">
            <li>Curriculum input</li>
            <li>A dedicated privacy-preserving AI assistant for your own knowledge management</li>
            <li>Additional one-on-one and group support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="funding-block">
        <h3 class="block-title">Web3 Sponsorship</h3>
        <p class="block-amount">USD $25,000–$50,000</p>
        <p class="block-description">
          From Near Protocol, Anoma, Celo, and comparable networks.
        </p>
        <div class="benefits">
          <p class="benefits-label">Sponsors receive:</p>
          <ul class="benefits-list">
            <li>Content input and live access to Alliance members</li>
            <li>Brand placement in relevant sessions</li>
            <li>Free Bioregional Builder slots for Canada-based AI infrastructure projects</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="labor-note">
      Resources governed through a purpose-built, time-limited DAO. All
      financial flows on public distributed ledgers. Labor contributed by
      Green Pill Network, Bread Cooperative, OpenCivics Labs, and Gaia AI.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .resourcing {
    background-color: var(--color-cream-light);
    padding-block: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .target {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.85;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: none;
  }

  .funding-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .funding-block {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background-color: rgba(237, 221, 200, 0.5);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.06);
  }

  .block-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 0.15em;
  }

  .block-amount {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    max-width: none;
  }

  .block-description {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.85;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    max-width: none;
  }

  .benefits {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background-color: rgba(237, 221, 200, 0.6);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-orange);
  }

  .benefits-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    max-width: none;
  }

  .benefits-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .benefits-list li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.85;
    padding-block: var(--space-xs);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .benefits-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .labor-note {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.6;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 70ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .resourcing {
      padding-block: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .funding-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }

    .funding-block {
      padding: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
